  <dt>2019 September 6th-8th ‚Äî <a href="http://www.samuel-drapeau.info/conference-2019-09/">Conference on Stochastic Analysis, Stochastic Dynamical Systems and Stochastic Finance</a></dt>
  <dd><strong>Date:</strong> September 6th‚Äì8th<br />
<strong>Place:</strong> <a href="http://math.sjtu.edu.cn/en">School of Mathematical Sciences</a>, <a href="http://www.sjtu.edu.cn/">Shanghai Jiao Tong University</a>, Dongchuan Road 800, Shanghai <br />
