<strong>Title:</strong> Geometry of the Skorokhod embedding problem <br />
<strong>Abstract:</strong>Most of this talk is devoted to explain the results of  ‚ÄúOptimal Transport and Skorokhod Embedding‚Äù by Beiglboeck, Cox, and Huesmann. If time permits, we talk about some recent progress together with Mathias Beiglboeck and Manu Eder.     <br />
