<strong>Organizers:</strong>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://math.maths.univ-evry.fr/crepey/">St√©phane Crepey (University of Evry)</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://www.math.nus.edu.sg/~matdm/">Min DAI (National University of Singapore)</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://www.samuel-drapeau.info">Samuel Drapeau (Shanghai Jiao Tong University)</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://www.rmi.nus.edu.sg/aboutus/profile/stevenkou/stevenkou.html">Steven KOU (National University of Singapore)</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://www.normalesup.org/~athiery/">Alexandre Thiery (National University of Singapore)</a></li>
